A woman threw her husband's body into a pit and poured concrete near Belgorod
In the Belgorod region, a woman confessed to the murder of her own husband, whom she threw into a waste pit and poured concrete into, according to the website of the regional administration of the IC of the Russian Federation.
It is noted that the suspect has been married to the deceased since 1999.
In recent years, the husband began to abuse alcohol and, after another quarrel, the woman decided to kill.
"When the husband fell asleep, the suspect tied his hands and legs, put a plastic bag over his head and pressed him with a pillow.
