The next day, she called a concrete mixer and poured concrete into the pit, "the department said.
The woman later reported that her husband had disappeared.
Relatives of the deceased contacted police, who opened the hole and removed the body.
The investigation intends to ask the court to arrest the suspect.
The criminal investigation is currently underway.
